  <brief_title>Denosumab Versus Bisphosphonates (Alendronate) in GIOP</brief_title>
  <official_title>Denosumab Versus Oral Bisphosphonate (Alendronate) for Osteoporosis in Long-term Glucocorticoid Users: an Open Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
